-------------------------------------------------------------
---Simple Address Book Program that takes 4 Records---
-------------------------------------------------------------
1-Create / Update Record                                              //Create & Update
2-Get All Records                                                     //Get
3-Get Specific Record                                                 //Sorting by name (Still Working on this operation)
4-Exit                                                                //Exit
-------------------------------------------------------------
1
--Option 1 selected--
1(1)-Create/Update 1st Record
1(2)-Create/Update 2nd Record
1(3)-Create/Update 3rd Record
1(4)-Create/Update 4th Record
-------------------------------------------------------------
